rows.label: qst000802_msg0001
rows.name:
Yo! Meeting here must be
fate! Let's chat for a bit.

rows.label: qst000802_msg0003
rows.name:
Following in my grandpa's footsteps,
I'm a treasure hunter who travels
all over Alst for treasure!

rows.label: qst000802_msg0101
rows.name:
Erebos-san? Could you be
the one from the knife...?
We were looking for you!

rows.label: qst000802_msg0102
rows.name:
Erebos-san? Could you be
the one from the knife...?
We were looking for you!

rows.label: qst000802_msg0103
rows.name:
Erebos? Could you be the
one from that knife...?
We've been looking for you!

rows.label: qst000802_msg0104
rows.name:
Erebos-san, mo? Could you be from
that knife...? We found you, mo~!

rows.label: qst000802_msg0105
rows.name:
Erebos? Could you be from that
knife...? We finally meet.

rows.label: qst000802_msg0106
rows.name:
Erebos? Could you be from that
knife...? We were looking for you!

rows.label: qst000802_msg0202
rows.name: You brought it... D-don't tell me!!

rows.label: qst000802_msg0203
rows.name:
You're here to give me a one-way
ticket to the afterlife...

rows.label: qst000802_msg0204
rows.name:
and steal my grandpa's
treasure and everything else!

rows.label: qst000802_msg0205
rows.name:
No more talk! My grandpa's
motto was to be wary of sweet
words and free food!!
